---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Process - Enablement Engineering" description="Learn about our collaborative approach to building capabilities and enabling teams">
	<!-- Hero Section -->
		<section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-6">
				<h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-ink leading-tight">
					Our Process
				</h1>
				<p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
					A collaborative, iterative approach designed to maximize impact while minimizing risk and uncertainty.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Process Steps -->
		<section class="py-16">
			<div class="space-y-16">
				<!-- Step 1 -->
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
					<div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
						<div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-6">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
								<span class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-600">1</span>
							</div>
							<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-ink">Discovery & Assessment</h2>
						</div>
						<p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
							We begin every engagement by thoroughly understanding your current state, challenges, and objectives. This phase involves stakeholder interviews, system analysis, and goal alignment to ensure we're solving the right problems.
						</p>
						<ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-600">
							<li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
								<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary-400 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
								<span>Stakeholder interviews and needs assessment</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
								<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary-400 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
								<span>Current system and process analysis</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
								<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary-400 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
								<span>Goal definition and success criteria</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
						<div class="card-base p-8 off-kilter-0-5">
							<div class="w-full h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-primary-200 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
								<div class="text-primary-600 text-6xl font-bold">üîç</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Step 2 -->
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
					<div class="order-1">
						<div class="card-base p-8 off-kilter-neg-0-5">
							<div class="w-full h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-100 to-accent-200 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
								<div class="text-accent-600 text-6xl font-bold">üé®</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="order-2">
						<div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-6">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
								<span class="text-xl font-bold text-accent-600">2</span>
							</div>
							<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-ink">Design & Planning</h2>
						</div>
						<p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
							Working collaboratively, we design solutions that fit your specific context, constraints, and culture. This phase emphasizes co-creation to ensure buy-in and sustainable adoption.
						</p>
						<ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-600">
							<li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
								<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-accent-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
								<span>Collaborative solution design workshops</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
								<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-accent-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
								<span>Architecture and implementation planning</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
								<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-accent-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
								<span>Risk assessment and mitigation strategies</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Step 3 -->
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
					<div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
						<div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-6">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-secondary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
								<span class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary-600">3</span>
							</div>
							<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-ink">Implementation</h2>
						</div>
						<p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
							We implement solutions iteratively, delivering value in manageable increments. This approach allows for continuous feedback and adjustment while maintaining momentum.
						</p>
						<ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-600">
							<li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
								<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-secondary-600 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
								<span>Iterative development and deployment</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
								<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-secondary-600 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
								<span>Regular progress reviews and adjustments</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
								<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-secondary-600 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
								<span>Quality assurance and testing</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
						<div class="card-base p-8 off-kilter-0-5">
							<div class="w-full h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary-100 to-secondary-200 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
								<div class="text-secondary-600 text-6xl font-bold">‚öôÔ∏è</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Step 4 -->
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
					<div class="order-1">
						<div class="card-base p-8 off-kilter-neg-0-5">
							<div class="w-full h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-accent-200 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
								<div class="text-primary-600 text-6xl font-bold">üöÄ</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="order-2">
						<div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-6">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
								<span class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-600">4</span>
							</div>
							<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-ink">Launch & Enable</h2>
						</div>
						<p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
							The final phase focuses on successful adoption and ongoing success. We provide training, documentation, and support to ensure your team can confidently operate and evolve the solution.
						</p>
						<ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-600">
							<li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
								<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary-400 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
								<span>Team training and knowledge transfer</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
								<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary-400 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
								<span>Documentation and runbooks</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
								<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary-400 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
								<span>Ongoing support and optimization</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Principles -->
		<section class="py-16 bg-neutral-50 rounded-2xl off-kilter-0-5">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-12">
				<div class="text-center space-y-6">
					<h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-ink">Our Principles</h2>
					<p class="text-xl text-neutral-600">
						These core principles guide every engagement and decision we make.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
					<div class="space-y-6">
						<div class="space-y-3">
							<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Collaborative Partnership</h3>
							<p class="text-neutral-600">We work with you, not for you. Your team's involvement and input are essential to creating solutions that stick.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="space-y-3">
							<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Iterative Value Delivery</h3>
							<p class="text-neutral-600">We believe in delivering value early and often, allowing for course correction and continuous improvement.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="space-y-3">
							<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Sustainable Solutions</h3>
							<p class="text-neutral-600">Our focus is on building capabilities that your team can maintain and evolve long after our engagement ends.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-6">
						<div class="space-y-3">
							<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Context-Aware Design</h3>
							<p class="text-neutral-600">We recognize that every organization is unique. Our solutions are tailored to your specific context and constraints.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="space-y-3">
							<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Knowledge Transfer</h3>
							<p class="text-neutral-600">We're committed to enabling your team with the knowledge and skills needed to succeed independently.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="space-y-3">
							<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Transparent Communication</h3>
							<p class="text-neutral-600">We maintain open, honest communication throughout the engagement, sharing both successes and challenges.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
</Layout>